{
  "stem": "22750.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was always, I don't want to mention name, I take the credit-- aggressive in my life and the way I was at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they asked me, you have a wife and kid?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I had to answer, what I will do if I take my wife with me?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would be better?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not doing this for pleasure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the end, they came and took my wife with my kid, because I was working two sides.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I find a place, also, in case when it came, I always prepared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a decent life, in my life for myself, to survive and to support myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you were most concerned about the safety of your wife and your son?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the last day, I took my wife and my child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't let out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only because I was a Judenrat-- and I brought them to the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because I was a Judenrat with the protection from the inside, they let me out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took it out right away, the stars, my wife and him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they went out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I talked to him, this was our discussion-- as, in case I will be lucky to came before night, to find them there and there by a river between-- in a big, you know, hole.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we will find each other, in case we will be lucky to find each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want to ask me something else?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I talk too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what came to my mind, the reason, I am the subject for you talking to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd like to explain the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
